body:
We are Looking for:

An experienced Front-End developer to join our team.

The Project:

The project consists of implementing a multi-functional interface for an electric bike (eBike) that was launched on the market last year. Among the features of the gadget are: high quality design, large color display, ability to download and install new applications, security, automated system for updates check, communication with mobile devices, synchronization with the online, gps, navigation, offline maps.

The client of this project is a global supplier of technology and services for the industrial, consumer goods and automotive sectors.

Responsibilities:

# Requirements analysis
# Design document creation
# Application implementation
# Code reviews and bug fixing
# Progress reporting

Competencies:

Must have:

# Front-End experience: JavaScript, Ajax; JSON; REST APIs; jQuery; HTML5, CSS3 knowledge; CSS preprocessors (SASS, LESS); Grid system knowhow
# Fluency in English

Nice to have:

# Client side framework experience (Angular.js)
# Cross browsers issues experience
# Web APIs
# Single Page Application
# Continuous Integration practices
# Agile/Scrum methodologies working experience
# GIT experience
# Atlassian tools (JIRA, Confluence) know-how
# Web mobile experience (media queries, browser compatibility)
# Conversational skills in German

We Value:

# Respect
# Reliability
# Striving for excellence

Notes:

Only candidates selected after the CV screening phase will be contacted.

The position is in Cluj-Napoca, but we also recruit non-Cluj residents willing to relocate. 





			    $(document).ready(function() { 
			    var allVideos = $('.job-video-container object, .job-video-container embed, .job-video-container iframe'); 
			    var oldWidth = allVideos.width();
			    var oldHeight =  allVideos.height();
			    var aspectRatioOS = oldHeight/oldWidth; 
			    allVideos.removeAttr('height').removeAttr('width');
			    function resizeVideoOSJS(){
				allVideos.attr('style', 'max-width: 600px; width: 100%;');
				var widthInit = allVideos.width();
				var heightInit = widthInit * aspectRatioOS;
				allVideos.attr('style', 'max-width: 600px; width: 100%; min-height: 220px; height: '+ heightInit +'px;');
				//.attr('width',  widthInit).attr('height', allVideos.height())    
			    }
			    resizeVideoOSJS();
				    window.onresize = resizeVideoOSJS; 
			    });
